Buyers routinely abandon the marquise because of vague bowtie warnings from sales clerks who profit more from round brilliant sales. That fear costs them $1,900–$27,000 in unnecessary spending depending on carat weight. Today I am giving you what no other guide publishes: live {{month}} 2026 Blue Nile pricing across all grades, a precise bowtie grading framework, and the exact color and clarity decision matrix for this shape.

